      <title>随着农村地区生育率下降，医院产房纷纷关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/07/12/nx-s1-5036878/rural-hospitals-labor-delivery-health-care-shortage-birth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一些农村地区，自 20 世纪 50 年代末以来，出生率下降了四分之三，医院纷纷关闭产房，导致母亲在需要护理时几乎无法获得护理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/07/12/nx-s1-5036878/rural-hospitals-labor-delivery-health-care-shortage-birth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
